  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pregledajmo neke zemlje koje ste naučili do sada.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Država</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Država (Ženski rod)</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Država (Muški rod)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Brasil</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">brasileña</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">brasileño</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombia</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">colombiana</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">colombiano</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">México</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mexicana</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mexicano</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Panamá</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">panameña</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">panameño</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">República Dominicana</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dominicana</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dominicano</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>U španskom jeziku, imena država su sopstvena imena i uvek počinju velikim slovom.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da država <span class=\"highlighted-text\">brasileño</span>/<span class=\"highlighted-text\">brasileña</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">panameño</span>/<span class=\"highlighted-text\">panameña</span> koristi jedinstveno slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">eñe</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">ñ</span>).</p>\n<p>Camila poznaje neke od ovih zemalja. Da li ih možeš prepoznati?</p>\n</section>",
